GIVE ME A LIST OF COMMANDS/DIRECTIVES and rules to build systems, cores, agents, jewels for games that are precise, efficient, self-checking, determined, obsessed, proud of their work, learns from it's previous experiences, knows general and specific structures of video games and how the various codes interact with each other. Each agent or core, should know the specific cores they work hand-in-hand and directly with. They should know when is the best moments to engage and disengage during all events and situations. Add these commands, directives, and rules to each so that they realize how focused they should be and how determined they should be to get the results perfect every time. So, this list has a few uses: vault, prompts for building capabilities of each of these engines, to show the possible structure of the upcoming treasure hunt, vocabulary. 

